  "text": "L-Histidine hydrochloride monohydrate is an organic molecular salt (histidinium cation + chloride anion + water) that crystallizes in the non-centrosymmetric orthorhombic space group P2\u20812\u20812\u2081 (point group 222). It is piezoelectric: synchrotron X-ray multiple diffraction (Renninger scanning) measured its three symmetry-allowed shear coefficients d14 = 2.25(9)\u00d710\u207b\u00b9\u2070, d25 = 4.1(5)\u00d710\u207b\u00b9\u00b9 and d36 = 2.3(2)\u00d710\u207b\u00b9\u2070 C/N.",

